WEBVTT

00:06:29.319 --> 00:06:32.069
we discovered that we really
liked each other

00:06:32.093 --> 00:06:35.477
and we really liked spending
a lot of time with each other.

00:06:36.090 --> 00:06:41.130
That began an exceptional collaboration
that lasted about 12 years.

00:06:41.841 --> 00:06:43.345
CA: So give us a hint of it,

00:06:43.369 --> 00:06:46.695
because the core of the papers
that you were publishing back then

00:06:46.719 --> 00:06:49.960
were around human decision-making

00:06:49.984 --> 00:06:54.664
and the many ways that we kind of
get it wrong, in a sense.

00:06:54.688 --> 00:06:55.839
Is that right?

00:06:55.863 --> 00:07:00.779
DK: Well, we started out asking
about judgment under uncertainty,